briefdescription.para: Cereal does not support the serialization of raw pointer.

detaileddescription.para: This macro enable developers to serialize std vectors that holds raw pointers by using the above PointerVectorWrapper class which replace the internal raw pointers by smart pointer internally.

parameterdescription.para: std::vector that holds raw pointer to be serialized.

detaileddescription.para: Omar Shrit Implementation of a vector wrapper to enable the serialization of the size of the vector in cereal
